title: Ep. 1072 - Bhide Breaks The Phone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sonu's phone broke as Bhide didn't hand it over properly. They try fixing it but the phone doesn't switch on. They eagerly wait for it to start working properly again.

title: Ep. 1073 - Funny Pcitures - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha has a problem with kids using phones as it is creating trouble for him. When asked, he shows the funny pictures and editing that has happened to all the pictures.

title: Ep. 1074 - Goli Scares His Friend - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Goli and his friends are scaring one of Goli's friends by calling up in the night. The friends and his parents have come to Gokukdham to complain against the same to their parents.

title: Ep. 1075 - Babita's Advice To Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha runs behind Tapu and encounters Babita in between. While conversing, Babita tells Jetha to exercise regularly.

title: Ep. 1076 - Where Are The Cellphones? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu and his friends come near their society worried about their life. They do not have their cellphones and they do not want their parents to know about it under any conditions.

title: Ep. 1077 - Jetha Is Distracted - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha asks Tapu about the phone and when Tapu refuses to answer and runs instead, Jetha chases him. However, he gets distracted when Babita calls him.

title: Ep. 1078 - Taarak Spots The Kids - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak and Anjali are in the garden when the Tapu Sena is bunking their school. When the kids see that Taarak and Anjali are in the garden, they make a run for their lives.

title: Ep. 1079 - Tapu Sena Exposed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After Taarak and Anjali tell the parents about their kids, the parents decide to go and see the principal of the school. Tapu Sena's lie is exposed.

title: Ep. 1080 - Forgiveness - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After the lie is caught, Tapu Sena comes to the school where they see their parents going through punishment for them. WIll the parents forgive their children?

title: Ep. 1081 - The Chocolate Pill - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha's knee is painful for which he must take the medicines. However, Daya gives him chocolate pills instead of his medicines by mistake.

title: Ep. 1082- The Water Problem - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As the Gokuldham society faces a water crisis, their only hope is Bhide and his tactics. Meanwhile, Bhide is busy in buying vegetables.

title: Ep. 1083 - The Broken Lock - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The society sees that there is a broken lock in the staircase of a building and someone has locked themself from inside. However, they are not able to figure out who it exactly is.

title: Ep. 1084 - The Unexpected Patient - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The society members are on the terrace of their buildings when Daya finds an unknown woman lying unconscious.

title: Ep. 1085 - English Lessons - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha signs on some papers that Natu Kaka brings to him and asks him for tea. As soon as Jetha demands tea, Bagha comes running with a cup of tea.

title: Ep. 1086 - Bharti Is Ready - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After the ladies of Gokuldham society find out the reason behind an unknown woman being in their society, they tell her - Bharti that it is important to fight back and Daya tells her the plan of doing so.
